    {
      "id": "69a483aa0000000000b0fca2",
      "text": "yeredere",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389291,
      "updated": 1772389294
    },
    {
      "id": "69a48048c8150291db8c76ee",
      "text": "日：[イェレデレ][. ［要出典］]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388430,
      "updated": 1772389454
    },
    {
      "id": "69a484560000000000b0fca3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389462,
      "updated": 1772389462
    },
    {
      "id": "69a480580000000000b0fc86",
      "text": "英語圏で使用例のあるサブカル用語。 #ヤンデレ の亜種らしい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388440,
      "updated": 1772389462
    },
    {
      "id": "69a480680000000000b0fc87",
      "text": "\tなぜか日本語が語源であるかのようになっているが、[英製和語]である",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388456,
      "updated": 1772389620
    },
    {
      "id": "69a481310000000000b0fc89",
      "text": "\t同義語として[/ [ヤンヒート]] (Yanheat) があるらしい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388658,
      "updated": 1772389161
    },
    {
      "id": "69a481870000000000b0fc8c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388744,
      "updated": 1772388744
    },
    {
      "id": "69a482e90000000000b0fc94",
      "text": "[Yanheat | Dere Types Wiki | Fandom https://the-dere-types.fandom.com/wiki/Unofficial:Yanheat]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389098,
      "updated": 1772389109
    },
    {
      "id": "69a483380000000000b0fc95",
      "text": "\ttable: ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389176,
      "updated": 1772389579
    },
    {
      "id": "69a484c80000000000b0fca4",
      "text": " \tDere Type:\tGapless",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389577,
      "updated": 1772389591
    },
    {
      "id": "69a483390000000000b0fc97",
      "text": "  Japanese Name:\tヤンヒート",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389178,
      "updated": 1772389591
    },
    {
      "id": "69a483390000000000b0fc99",
      "text": "  Romanized Name:\tYanheat, Yeredere",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389187,
      "updated": 1772389591
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4834e0000000000b0fc9c",
      "text": " ページ履歴",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389199,
      "updated": 1772389205
    },
    {
      "id": "69a482c50000000000b0fc92",
      "text": " \t> 20:11, 3 November 2024 Black60dragon Message Wall contribs m  3,555 bytes 0  Black60dragon moved page Unofficial:[Yeredere] to Unofficial:[Yanheat]: ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389062,
      "updated": 1772389426
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4836e0000000000b0fc9e",
      "text": "  > Renaming \"Yeredere\" since being a combination of any [dere type]+[deredere] doesn't make any sense. This is now a combination of [yandere] and [sunao] heat (the Japanese equivalent of Western [megadere])",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389230,
      "updated": 1772389638
    },
    {
      "id": "69a482c50000000000b0fc93",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389062,
      "updated": 1772389062
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4818c0000000000b0fc8d",
      "text": "\t[What is a Yandere? Everything You Need to Know | WikiHow https://www.wikihow.com/Yandere-Meaning]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388749,
      "updated": 1772388790
    },
    {
      "id": "69a481ce0000000000b0fc8f",
      "text": "\t> Yeredere",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388815,
      "updated": 1772388817
    },
    {
      "id": "69a481d10000000000b0fc90",
      "text": " > Yeredere characters have the classic obsessive qualities of a [yandere] without any of their violent [tendencies]. Think of them as the characters who do all sorts of chores and favors for their love interest, like making them meals, sending them gifts, and so on.",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388817,
      "updated": 1772389406
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4814e0000000000b0fc8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772388687,
      "updated": 1772388687
    },
    {
      "id": "69a483880000000000b0fc9f",
      "text": "類義語",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389256,
      "updated": 1772389261
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4838d0000000000b0fca1",
      "text": "\t[megadere] ([/ メガデレ])",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772389262,
      "updated": 1772389285
    },
